    </ul>
    <p>
      <b>Throw it Away</b><br/><br/>    
      Some items just need to be thrown away. They are junk, clear up your 
      home/office by sorting out these items, those that you know can't be sold 
      or given out should be thrown away, it's really as simple as that.
    </p>
